-- Batista to Sell 49% AUX Stake to Qatar for $2 Billion, Veja Says
-- B y   G a b r i e l l e   C o p p o l a
-- 2012-09-22T17:16:35Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-09-22/batista-to-sell-49-aux-stake-to-qatar-for-2-billion-veja-says.html
Brazilian billionaire  Eike Batista 
will announce soon the sale of a 49 percent stake in his AUX
gold business to a sovereign wealth fund in Qatar, Veja magazine
 reported  today, without saying how it obtained the information.  Bloomberg reported in June that Batista was planning to
sell a stake AUX to the Qatar Investment Authority for about $2
billion, citing a person with knowledge of the transaction.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Gabrielle Coppola in Sao Paulo at 
 gcoppola@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Sylvia Wier at 
 swier@bloomberg.net  